  Myrmidon frowned, not caring all that much to be laughed at, even if the humor was not derogatory, and even if it was from his new commander. He nodded as Hydras mentioned leaving, and gestured for Hydras to lead so that he may follow, even as Myrmidon silently wondered when he would meet these others of Hydras' followers. 
   
  Preston
